(NULL, 'MUSC', '027B', 'Fundamentals of Jazz Keyboard II', 'Advanced applications of materials presented in MUSC 27A, including keyboard performance of selected lead-sheet literature; chord symbol recognition, keyboard techniques, chord substitutions introduced, polychords. Prerequisite: MUSC 27A (or equivalent).'),
